		"description": "Description:\r\nDuring KitchenSink testing I noticed, that device's rotation causes changing size of a spinner. It happens when 2nd spinner scrolled down to an overlapped verb.\r\n\r\nThis is not a regression, the behavior occurs on 2.0.2 as well.\r\n\r\nSteps to reproduce:\r\n1. Run KitchenSink\r\n2. Go to Controls - Picker - Android \"useSpinner\"-text2\r\n3. Scroll down 2nd spinner with verbs until a word with overlapping\r\n4. Rotate device \r\n\r\nActual result:\r\nThe spinner changes size \r\n\r\nExpected result:\r\nThe spinner should not change size\r\n",
